@NODE intro "Introduction"
@{u}Introduction@{uu}

   Dunkie said "I want a log-off after downloads door but I don't want to use
MagicFile.", so this is it...  The download bit from MagicFile, for free! :o)
It started off as just the countdown, but I thought maybe I could release this
and tempt some people to buy MagicFile, or something, or maybe i'm just being
nice? :o)

Features

o  Pre-down Ratio gauge
o  Log-off after download option
o  Download individual files as well as normal download
o  Transfer statistics (and big CPS)
o  Included screens for ISO users.

Doesn't feature

o  Byte ratio support in MAX's Pro 2
o  Uploads before downloads and some other features from MagicFile
o  Configurable text/colours
o  Nice documentation!

Want these features? Buy MagicFile!

@{u}Requirements@{uu}

MAX's BBS 1.54 68000 version or MAX's Pro.
That's it really!

@ENDNODE


